name: Hustlin' Broke Witch
description:
Witch needs some money. Cast crazy spells and try to get famous and a good reputation to be able to enter the Academe. A simple game for the Themed Horror Game Jam #9 - Halloween Edition. 

Finished 3 am so dazed but making this was SO fun!

Assets are recolored GB studio default assets,

'Door' is from Smoke Oak from Open Game Art

Included below is the downloadable version with the project folder. 

Made with GB Studio...
